There he is!

04:04.199 --> 04:06.266
This way!

04:09.103 --> 04:12.072
Hurry up!
Get him!

04:18.762 --> 04:21.298
Enough.

04:22.750 --> 04:24.584
Let him go.

04:26.888 --> 04:29.723
He's heading into
Chance Harbor.

04:29.725 --> 04:31.394
We're just going to
have to work faster.

